As the administrator of JIRA Service Desk, I would like the ability to configure the Service Desk mail channel to retrieve mail from the local file system.

The JIRA Core mail handlers are able to retrieve mail from the local file system but these mail handlers are not able to bypass the license and permission requirements so that customers can create and comment issues.
 * Additional details regarding the JIRA Core mail handlers are available in the "File system messages" section of [Creating issues and comments from email |https://confluence.atlassian.com/adminjiraserver071/creating-issues-and-comments-from-email-802592933.html]

